OL,4,CInstagram launches hate-speech 'limits'
OL,5,Cto hide abuse
OL,6, Instagram has announced new features
OL,7, designed to restrict hate speech during
OL,8, "sudden spikes" of abuse.
OL,10,FIts new "limits" feature automatically
OL,11,Fhides comments and messages from people
OL,12,Fwho do not follow - or just started
OL,13,Ffollowing - users who switch it on.
OL,15,FIt was designed to stop abuse from
OL,16,Flarge numbers of people "who simply
OL,17,Fpile on in the moment", Instagram said.
OL,19,FThe company specifically referenced the
OL,20,Fracist abuse following the men's Euro
OL,21,F2020 football final as one example.
